ChooseParameter.Other: The BT@PHEMA NPs were recovered after three cycles of DMF wash and centrifuging at 9000 rpm for 10 min.

Mixing.Description: To synthesize core@double-shell structured NPs, BT@PHEMA were redispersed in a flask containing a mixed solution of 20 mL DMF and 10 mL MMA, followed by 10 min sonication.

Additive.Description: 0.5 mmol CuBr (0.0715 g) and 0.1 mmol CuBr2 (0.0225 g) were added to the flask.
0.5 mmol CuBr (0.0715 g) and 0.1 mmol CuBr2 (0.0225 g) were added to the flask.
0.6 mmol PMDETA (0.104 g) was added via a syringe.

Mixing.Description: The mixture was stirred at 60 °C for 24 h.
